Cell c1 = new Cell(5);
Cell c2 = new Cell(5);
Cell c3 = c1;
boolean r1 = c1.equals(c2);
boolean r2 = c1 == c3;
boolean r3 = c1.equals(c3);
System.out.println(r1 + "/" + r2 + "/" + r3);
```

Optional と map()・orElse() の連鎖。次のコードの出力はどれか。

```java
import java.util.Optional;
String str = null;
Optional<String> opt = Optional.ofNullable(str);
String result = opt
    .map(s -> s.toUpperCase())
    .orElse(null);
boolean isPresent = opt.isPresent();
System.out.println(isPresent + ":" + result);
```

